column12:
'desc': [u'

Barbie Hand Gel (50 ml) Price: Rs.60

Children love being messy
column15:
paint and whatever they can find. It can be difficult to wash and clean your tiny tot’s hands when you cannot find soap and water especially when not at home. At such times the Barbie Hand Gel will come as a boon to you. This hand gel cleans your bundle of joy’s hands instantly without using water or soap. You will not have to run about for towels or hand driers.

The mild and effective formula of the Barbie Hand Gel kills germs substantially. The soft fragrance that lingers on your hands after using the Barbie Hand Gel will make you feel fresh and clean. This Hand Gel from Barbie is dermatologically tested and hence is safe to be used on your child’s delicate hands. It can be used by adults as well to clean and sanitize their hands when needed.
